#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kjumpingcube.appdata.xml:12
msgid ""
"KJumpingCube is a simple dice driven tactical game. The playing area "
"consists of squares containing points. Players move by clicking on either a "
"vacant square, or on own square."
msgstr ""
"KJumpingCube dadoak gidatutako taktika-joko bat da. Joko eremua, puntuak "
"dituzten karratuz osatuta dago. Jokalariek hutsik dagoen karratu batean edo "
"karratu propio batean klik eginez mugitzen dute."

